C]]<br/>{{flag|Qatar|size=23px}}<br/>{{flag|NATO|size=23px}}\n*{{flag|Belgium|size=23px}}\n*{{flag|Bulgaria|size=23px}}\n*{{flag|Canada|size=23px}}\n*{{flag|Denmark|size=23px}}\n*{{flag|France|size=23px}}\n*{{flag|Greece|size=23px}}\n*{{flag|Italy|size=23px}}\n*{{flag|Netherlands|size=23px}}\n*{{flag|Norway|size=23px}}\n*{{flag|Romania|size=23px}}\n*{{flag|Spain|size=23px}}\n*{{flag|Turkey|size=23px}}\n*{{flag|United Kingdom|size=23px}}\n*{{flag|United States|size=23px}}\n{{flag|Sweden|size=23px}}<br/>{{flag|Jordan|size=23px}}<br/>{{nowrap|{{flag|United Arab Emirates|size=23px}}}}\n| {{flagicon|Libyan Arab Jamahiriya|1977|size=23px}} [[History of Libya under Muammar Gaddafi#Great Socialist People's Libyan Arab Jamahiriya (1977\u20132011)|Libya]]\n| '''Victory'''\n* Overthrow of [[Muammar Gaddafi]] in Libya\n* [[Death of Muammar Gaddafi]]\n* Dissolution of the [[Libyan Arab Jamahiriya]]\n| '''None'''\n| '''None'''\n|-\n| [[Military intervention against the Islamic State of Iraq and the Levant|Military intervention against<br/>the Islamic State of Iraq and the Levant]]<br/>(2014&ndash;present)\n| \n{{flag|United States|size=23px}}<br/>\n{{flag|United Kingdom|size=23px}}<br/>\n{{flag|Australia|size=23px}}<br/>\n{{flag|Belgium|size=23px}}<br/>\n{{flag|Canada|size=23px}}<br/>\n{{flag|Denmark|size=23px}}<br/>\n{{flag|France|size=23px}}<br/>\n{{flag|Germany|size=23px}}<br/>\n{{flag|Italy|size=23px}}<br/>\n{{flag|Netherlands|size=23px}}<br/>\n{{flag|New Zealand|size=23px}}<br/>\n{{flag|Norway|size=23px}}<br/>\n{{flag|Portugal|size=23px}}<br/>\n{{flag|Spain|size=23px}}<br/>\n{{flag|Sweden|size=23px}}<br/>\n{{flag|Turkey|size=23px}}<br/>\n| {{flag|Islamic State of Iraq and the Levant|size=23px}}\n| '''Ongoing'''\n* Airstrikes on ISIL and al-Qaeda affiliates positions in Iraq and Syria\n* Multinational humanitarian effort\n* Arming and support for local ground forces\n* 2 American journalists, 2 British humanitarian workers, and 1 French tourist executed<ref>{{cite web|url=htt