nadas]], etc.), and/or First Nations groups residing in these region. \n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"background:#efefef;\"\n|-\n! Conflict\n! Combatant 1\n! Combatant 2\n! Result\n|-\n| [[Beaver Wars]]<br>(1609\u20131701)\n| [[Iroqouis]]\n| [[Algonquian peoples|Algonquian]] allies\n| '''Military stalemate'''\n* [[Great Peace of Montreal]]\n* Growth of French influence in the Great Lakes region\n* Huron-Wendat Confederacy destroyed or assimilated\n* Military refugee migration results in expansion of Iroquois hunting grounds\n* Further Iroquois territorial expansion halted in military campaigns by the [[Council of Three Fires]]\n|-\n| [[King William's War]]<br>(1688\u20131697)\n| {{flag|Kingdom of France}}\n* {{flag|New France}}\n[[Wabanaki Confederacy]]\n| {{flag|England}}\n* {{flagdeco|England}} [[British America|English America]]\n[[Iroquois]]\n|'''''Status quo ante bellum'''''\n|-\n| [[Queen Anne's War]]<br>(1702\u20131713)\n| {{flag|Kingdom of France}}\n* {{flag|New France}}\n{{flag|Spain|1701}}<br>[[Wabanaki Confederacy]]<br>[[Mohawk people|Caughnawaga Mohawk]]<br>[[Choctaw]]<br>[[Timucua]]<br>[[Apalachee]]<br>[[Natchez]]\n| {{flag|England}} <small>(before 1707)</small>\n* {{flagdeco|England}} [[British America|English America]]\n{{flag|Great Britain|1707}} <small>(after 1707)</small>\n* {{flagdeco|British Empire|1707}} [[British America]]\n[[Muscogee people|Muscogee]]<br>[[Chickasaw]]<br>[[Yamasee]]\n----\n[[Iroquois Confederacy]]\n|'''British-Allied victory'''\n* France cedes to Britain the control of Acadia, Newfoundland, Hudson Bay, and Saint Kitts\n|-\n| [[Dummer's War]]<br>(1722\u20131725)\n| [[New England Colonies]]<br>[[Mohawk]]\n| [[Wabanaki Confederacy]]<br>[[Abenaki]]<br>[[Pequawket]]<br>[[Mi'kmaq]]<br>[[Maliseet]]\n|\n|-\n| [[King George's War]]<br>(1744\u20131748)\n| {{flag|Kingdom of France}}\n* {{flag|New France}}\n[[Wabanaki Confederacy]]\n| {{flag|British Empire|1707}}\n* {{flagdeco|British Empire|1707}} [[British America]]\n[[Iroquois Confede