px}}<br/>{{flag|Turkey|size=23px}}<br/>{{flag|Afghanistan|size=23px}}<br/>{{flagicon|Afghanistan|1992|size=23px}} [[Northern Alliance]]<br/>{{collapsible list\n| bullets = yes\n| title = {{nowrap|{{flagicon image|Flag of the International Security Assistance Force.svg|size=23px}} [[International Security Assistance Force|ISAF]]}}\n|{{flag|Albania|size=23px}}\n|{{flag|Armenia|size=23px}}\n|{{flag|Austria|size=23px}}\n|{{flag|Azerbaijan|size=23px}}\n|{{flag|Bahrain|size=23px}}\n|{{flag|Belgium|size=23px}}\n|{{flag|Bosnia and Herzegovina|size=23px}}\n|{{flag|Bulgaria|size=23px}}\n|{{flag|Croatia|size=23px}}\n|{{flag|Czech Republic|size=23px}}\n|{{flag|Denmark|size=23px}}\n|{{flag|El Salvador|size=23px}}\n|{{flag|Estonia|size=23px}}\n|{{flag|Finland|size=23px}}\n|{{flag|Greece|size=23px}}\n|{{flag|Hungary|size=23px}}\n|{{flag|Iceland|size=23px}}\n|{{flag|Ireland|size=23px}}\n|{{flag|Jordan|size=23px}}\n|{{flag|Latvia|size=23px}}\n|{{flag|Lithuania|size=23px}}\n|{{flag|Luxembourg|size=23px}}\n|{{flag|Malaysia|size=23px}}\n|{{flag|Mongolia|size=23px}}\n|{{flag|Montenegro|size=23px}}\n|{{flag|Netherlands|size=23px}}\n|{{flag|Norway|size=23px}}\n|{{flag|Portugal|size=23px}}\n|{{flag|Republic of Macedonia|size=23px}}\n|{{flag|Singapore|size=23px}}\n|{{flag|Slovakia|size=23px}}\n|{{flag|Slovenia|size=23px}}\n|{{flag|South Korea|size=23px}}\n|{{flag|Spain|size=23px}}\n|{{flag|Sweden|size=23px}}\n|{{flag|Switzerland|size=23px}}\n|{{flag|Tonga|size=23px}}\n|{{flag|Ukraine|size=23px}}\n|{{flag|United Arab Emirates|size=23px}}\n}}\n| {{flagicon|Afghanistan|Taliban|size=23px}} [[Taliban]]<br>{{flagicon image|Flag of al-Qaeda.svg|size=23px}} [[al-Qaeda]]<br>{{flagicon image|Flag of Jihad.svg|size=23px}} [[Islamic Movement of Uzbekistan]]<br>{{flagicon image|Flag of Jihad.svg|size=23px}} [[Hezb-e-Islami Gulbuddin|HI-Gulbuddin]]<br>{{flagicon image|Flag of Jihad.svg|size=23px}} [[Hezb-e Islami Khalis]]<br>{{flagicon image|Flag of Jihad.svg|size=23px}} [[Haqqani network]]<br>{{flagicon